items: Dimension: 183cm long x 68cm width x 4mm thick (2.7kg)
Materials: SGS-certified natural rubber, non-toxic vegan leather
Care:
Gently wipe the mat with a damp cloth after each use
Do not use oil-based cleaning products
Air dry the mat before rolling
Store out of direct sunlight and heat source
